snippet.textDisplay:
You ever have that feeling that your heart just broke into a thousand pieces, like a dropped martini glass on concrete? 

Well, imagine that, but then having those pieces WALKED ALL OVER by iron-studded boots caked in mud, gum, and dog turd.

That's what I feel like. My enjoyment, my caring for Woods, the Masons, the Black Ops universe as a whole, just...hurting me.

What was even the POINT of caring if this is what happens to my favorite characters?
